# TypeScript & React

```typescript
// ✅ Repository returns typed domain objects
const elements = await elementRepo.getAllElements(db);

// ❌ UI calling SQL
await db.runAsync('INSERT INTO elements ...');
```

- Parse external/JSON data with Zod (`parseElementDefinition`, `parseProtocolBundle`).
- Use `unknown` + narrow; never `any`.
- Async errors: catch, set store error state or rethrow with context.
- Prefer `void action()` in JSX handlers for floating promises.
